thread.title_full: Skipper (formerly Jetaport) reviewed by Breanna Dominguez

author: Breanna Dominguez
title: Breanna Dominguez
text: Skipper made it super easy for me to compare hotel block options and pick the ones that are best for my guests. I was dreading all the emailing and calling to book hotel blocks but Skipper took care of all of it and took away all of my stress.
